hkgmoji\" /> ，想做番d關於Bio野"},{"pid":"83f90509f3f9055d14ea57cc99bfdbe2b6f351f0","tid":13770,"uid":9479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:20:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做takka mc清concept先再做lq學key point<br />\n利申：5* 認真回</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正解"},{"pid":"ad247b4be5ca1c0fd92d907b7a3538d67e7e5020","tid":13770,"uid":42041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實我覺得bio係理解重要過操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明晒自然就識答<br />\n<br />\n利申 冇操過bio5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最重要係完全明每一個細節位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁之後學到既野就可以用返係前面幾課<br />\n之後就可以有個complete story出返黎<br />\n<br />\n例如 <br />\n之前學過virus淨係可以感染到特定既host <br />\n但係唔知點解<br />\n之後再學返 <br />\n原來唔同cell表面係有唔同既receptor <br />\n<br />\n就可以知道原來隻virus因為淨係可以bind到某d specific既surface receptor，然後再inject佢既DNA/RNA入去，咁bind唔到就自然感染唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後因爲係自己理解而唔係死操<br />\n就自然記得耐，同埋無論個題型點變都會識答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac15b1371ef2c81e6b2bf6be7cb1925d94f041c","tid":13770,"uid":10284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>私補我都ok 最緊要有4 努力過程唔重要 最緊要結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有心讀唔收你錢教又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只要有個好結果 付出幾多我都唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天行健<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ae32055a28bb0a3cff9b7f9601cacca12a663a","tid":13770,"uid":10284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可以教 但要十二月中後 final<br />\n<br />\n利申 dse 5*</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有補開幾個學生，個個成績都有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你有心學，我義教又點話。<br />\n大學無讀bio覺得好後侮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，想做番d關於Bio野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係個句 只要拎到好成績 唔怕辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f0c6621e1491abbecee173f2a09de41f8f1da2","tid":13770,"uid":8042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:05:53.000Z","msg":"以為招sp <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上一頁"},{"pid":"e91eed8efea77c48723610627796930f62912a9f","tid":13770,"uid":10284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做takka mc清concept先再做lq學key point<br />\n利申：5* 認真回</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打解答先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76382ea32449b1c7870ce81f5a365ee76bf75fd","tid":13770,"uid":10284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:06:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實我覺得bio係理解重要過操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明晒自然就識答<br />\n<br />\n利申 冇操過bio5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最重要係完全明每一個細節位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁之後學到既野就可以用返係前面幾課<br />\n之後就可以有個complete story出返黎<br />\n<br />\n例如 <br />\n之前學過virus淨係可以感染到特定既host <br />\n但係唔知點解<br />\n之後再學返 <br />\n原來唔同cell表面係有唔同既receptor <br />\n<br />\n就可以知道原來隻virus因為淨係可以bind到某d specific既surface receptor，然後再inject佢既DNA/RNA入去，咁bind唔到就自然感染唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後因爲係自己理解而唔係死操<br />\n就自然記得耐，同埋無論個題型點變都會識答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長知識了唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf79e6d20bd55c6cc803b843def29857018605f","tid":13770,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:08:18.000Z","msg":"死背notes有4<br />\n操下卷會上到5<br />\n想有星就要睇理唔理解同運氣<br />\n舊年份卷難咗今年應該會容易翻啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：2016 5*"},{"pid":"d773b1796ccf8b631248e081156c34aff5ac0d45","tid":13770,"uid":34236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:34:32.000Z","msg":"首先係理解哂課程內容 清哂concept 或者你可以試下溫完就將成個mechanism用自己個口講/背出黎 之後對下課文睇下漏左咩point 其實你講到出黎就代表你大概都明啦<br />\n<br />\n之後就做past paper練習下 最重要都係操下<span style=\"color: red;\">答題技巧</span> 同埋一定要熟讀marking scheme 睇下邊d係重點字眼 同埋點答 做得多其實會發覺佢問黎問去都係果d野 答法都係大同小異 可以背定d 答題template<br />\n<br />\n利申: <span style=\"color: red;\">係床上溫</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2015 5**"},{"pid":"50aad0a49554349a11c62099f7f941e0f87da51e","tid":13770,"uid":120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>操past paper就夠<br />\n學校predict我拎2-3<br />\n而bio通常都好後考 果陣考晒其他科有5日比我溫<br />\n果5日瘋狂做past paper <br />\n最後拎左個4 我自己都估唔到 以為頂龍得3<br />\n利申：2016考生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係唔係應該理解哂明哂先操好啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我平時上堂老師講嘅野都算明嘅 <br />\n但係我平時測驗考試答題都好差 <br />\n可能係我唔識答題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過識唔識答題我覺得係Bio黎講都幾重要下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917b5be29d5886fc97b86f57d08450dea396e7fc","tid":13770,"uid":46823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:59:29.000Z","msg":"背熟書，操mc清concept已經4到<br />\n背野時將內容寫做flow chart/steps/table，咁就會易記<br />\n做long q要仔細睇題目諗佢要你答乜，然後跟分數答。對答案時都要仔細睇你答少/答錯啲乜，然後記低重點<br />\n基本上你肯努力同用岩方法已經有5<br />\nPS 2016 bio 5**"},{"pid":"6aeb175cf04de61f742fb8a9502bef88863794ad","tid":13770,"uid":3280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:21:20.000Z","msg":"一路做一路讀囉<br />\n對住本書死記爛讀聽日就會無曬<br />\n<br />\n做一題mc 唔識做千奇唔好睇答案<br />\n即刻開書/notes 搵答案<br />\n如果成課未讀既 即刻溫左個sub chapter 先再答條問題<br />\n無一題都咁做<br />\n<br />\nmc 千奇唔好撞岩左就唔去搵書 <br />\n<br />\n要4個choice 都明左點解3 個錯1 個岩<blockquote>引用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣好快有成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申AL A"},{"pid":"bb6b3c87ec7f35c157f858ba0acd8b8ed58744cc","tid":13770,"uid":10284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:29:03.000Z","msg":"明白哂咁多位巴打 有冇巴打可以私補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5cd72458eaf447249ffb382500965703e03945d","tid":13770,"uid":3700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:37:20.000Z","msg":"認真分topic操past paper mc可以對每個topic嘅concept了解得好啲，跟著再睇下marking scheme點答sq lq都應該夠拎4<br />\n<br />\n利申2016 bio 5,做緊asso仔"},{"pid":"68e76a2e971d35fc36bb42c13008e4f9c45353d3","tid":13770,"uid":42795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我覺得bio係理解重要過操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明晒自然就識答<br />\n<br />\n利申 冇操過bio5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBio背書清concept背marking scheme緊要過做pp<br />\n答題一定要答中<strong>key words</strong><br />\n忌寫到水蛇春咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 DSE pp 無做曬 bio 5*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}